It's all in your head, Mr. Tweedy. Say it!

106
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:21,400
都是我想象的  都是我想象的
It's all in me head. It's all in me head

107
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:24,730
現在  你自己對自己重復
Now, you keep telling yourself that

108
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:27,570
因為我再也不想聽到它了
because I don't want to hear another word about it

109
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:30,870
- 清楚了嗎? - 清楚了  親愛的
- Is that clear? - Yes, love

110
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:32,900
但你知道那個姜妹...
