118
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:55,290
我請你們注意秩序...
I would like to call to order!Please

119
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:57,100
如果你們能夠...
if you could just...

120
00:14:57,170 --> 00:15:00,690
