124
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:08,190
是  謝謝你  福羅
Yes, thank you, Fowler

125
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:09,960
我...
I...

126
00:15:12,430 --> 00:15:14,660
對!
Right!

127
00:15:17,470 --> 00:15:19,370
